rComments: nice guy, cares about students, lectures are not boring

great prof! lectures are never boring because he always finds the best analogies/jokes to teach, and he genuinely wants us to do well. textbook isn't required, because you're not tested on it, but it's useful for clarification. he allows a good number of cheat sheets on exams so that's a plus too! overall 100/10 would def recommend.
